<title>Examples</title>
<simpara>Send cycles from the selected identity&#8217;s cycles wallet to another cycles wallet.</simpara>
<simpara>For example, to send 2,000,000,000 cycles from the cycles wallet of the selected identity, <literal>&lt;ic_admin&gt;</literal>, to the cycles wallet of the destination identity, <literal>&lt;buffy_standard&gt;</literal> with a wallet address <literal>r7inp-6aaaa-aaaaa-aaabq-cai</literal>, run the following command:</simpara>
<programlisting language="bash" linenumbering="unnumbered">dfx wallet send r7inp-6aaaa-aaaaa-aaabq-cai 2000000000</programlisting>
</section>
</section>
